<Content>Great Value/Helpful Staff We were recommended a different hotel on Avenue 5 de Mayo, however we found Hotel Canada and never looked back! The rooms are small, but clean and for AUD35 a night including breakfast, it was a great place to rest our heads at night.The staff there were more than happy to help us in any way they could and made our time in Mexico City much better.We hired a driver through the hotel called Eduardo (highly recommend him) and he drove us all around the city for a few days. We had our own private city tour. 
