<Content>A Decent Place to Stay in The Centro Historico Found the hotel whilst walking down Avenue 5 de Mayo and stumbled up the Hotel Canada. The rates are cheap, about $42.00 USD for a double room for two. The staff is helpful, friendly, and the rooms are also clean.My only suggestion: get a room by the street, for it is much cooler than the interior rooms. Safes are located in each room for your valuables. 
