<Content>Stay Here! I just got back from Mexico and while in Mexico City I stayed at the Hotel Canada. Just steps away from the Zocalo and many shops, restaurants, Alameda Park and the Palacio de Las Bellas Artes. After one night at another hotel (dark, dank, loud) I found this place (bright, friendly, clean and fairly quiet). For the price ($35 for a single), it was a steal considering the location. I'll definitely stay here my next trip!! 
